These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, poppy, zinnia
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
5. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Flower   | poppy | zinnia      | dahlia | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, mah-jongg, domino
1. the egyptian is between the person playing bridge and the person playing domino##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Game           | mah-jongg      | bridge    | chess | domino      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
4 different games are played: go, snooker, mah-jongg, billiard
1. the person eating corn is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
4. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Game   | snooker  | billiard   | mah-jongg | go    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, july, june
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in march##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Birthday   | june   | july     | march    | april       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, turtle, rat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Pet          | turtle | rat   | goat   | dog    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

