.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, old-henry, vegafina
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, thai, turkish
1. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the vegafina-smoker and the thai##2
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | siglo | vegafina | old-henry |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

