.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, singing, skydiving, chess
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is singing and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
5. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | baking  | skydiving  | chess   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

