.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
House: wooden, art-deco, futuristic, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| House   | art-deco     | farmhouse | futuristic     | wooden   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

