.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, mah-jongg, bridge
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pear, potato, tomato
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | domino | mah-jongg | bridge   | scrabble |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

