.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, fishing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, journalist, videographer, mechanic
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the videographer is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the journalist is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
5. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
6. the pilot is on the left or right of the journalist##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| Job   | journalist     | pilot | videographer  | mechanic |

