.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, bellflower, zinnia
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Flower   | zinnia  | iris | amaryllis | bellflower |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

