.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, watermelon, peach, onion
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
2. the person eating onion is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5
6. the person eating peach is between the person eating banana and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food      | banana   | peach  | watermelon      | onion       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

