The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, designer, videographer
1. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
2. the thai is the videographer##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the german##5
5. the designer is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german     | italian | turkish | thai |
| Job     | engineer | bartender    | designer    | videographer |

