.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, may, february
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
3. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday   | may | february  | november | september        |

