.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, blue, apricot, coral
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person who likes white is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who likes blue##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
3. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color         | apricot   | coral   | white       | blue   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

