.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, skateboarding, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is golf and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Sport        | volleyball     | golf | parkour | skateboarding |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 